			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/BGO_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe SAM_Combat\"\r\n- Locate the zombie with the \"Possessed\" status (initially it will be Sister Shirra). Get them down below half health without killing them.\r\n- On the possessed zombie's turn, the monk's ghost will leave that zombie, and enter the new zombie's body. This AD will then play on the newly possessed zombie."
				},
